# qidi-printer-mcp - Auto-trigger Rules

When the user asks about qidi printer, use qidi-printer-mcp tools: printer_status, get_temperatures, start_print, pause_print, resume_print

Controls QIDI 4 Max Combo (and other Klipper/Moonraker printers) via Moonraker REST API.

Install: `pip install qidi-printer-mcp`

